      boundary), ADR-021 (Fluent v9 + semantic tokens + dark-mode parity), ADR-022
      (React 19). Both gates MUST pass before marking the task complete.
    </step>
    <step order="10" name="Document + Complete">
      Update this task POML status to `complete`. Update `TASK-INDEX.md`: 013 🔲
